---
import ContentPageLayout from '../layouts/ContentPageLayout.astro';
---

<ContentPageLayout
  title="Contact Trees Puzzle | Editorial Questions and Partnerships"
  heading="Contact"
  description="Reach Trees Puzzle for editorial feedback, content corrections, classroom partnerships, or printable collaboration requests."
  canonicalPath="/contact/"
>
  <p>For editorial questions, correction requests, classroom collaborations, or partnership inquiries, use the email below.</p>
  <div class="bg-ink-900/60 border border-ink-700/50 rounded-2xl p-6">
    <p class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Editorial email</p>
    <p><a class="text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300 transition-colors" href="mailto:hello@treespuzzle.com">hello@treespuzzle.com</a></p>
  </div>
  <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white pt-4">What to include</h2>
  <p>If you are reporting a content issue, include the page URL and the correction you recommend. If you want to discuss a classroom or brand collaboration, include your timeline, audience, and what you need from the site.</p>
</ContentPageLayout>
